      right: ["Laryngeal edema (stridor, voice changes — emergency)", "No response to antihistamines, steroids, or epinephrine", "Low C1-INH level or function", "Attack triggered by trauma, surgery, or estrogen", "Abdominal attack mimicking acute abdomen"]
